				},
				"category": "defensive",
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The melodic squall is targeted by a spell with the auditory trait</p><hr><p><strong>Effect</strong> The melodic squall attempts to counteract the spell with a @Check[performance] check. If it succeeds, the spell effect is caught in a blast of wind that sweeps it back to its origin, affecting the caster. Targets of the triggering effect other than the melody on the wind are still affected normally.</p>",
