				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The melodic squall sings in a sonorous chorus. Any creature in a @Template[emanation|distance:30] must attempt a @Check[will|dc:36] save to resist becoming fascinated by the melody on the wind. A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune for 24 hours.</p><hr><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{Fascinated} for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{fascinated} for 4 rounds.</p>",
